医生端AJAX接口

修改个人账户：
    每个参数都不是必须，即不传代表不修改
POST /doc/modify_account
request:
    name:           <string>
    title:          <string>
    specialty:      <string>
    description:    <string>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>   // 0 - 成功
    message:        <string>
}

上传个人头像
POST /doc/upload_portrait
request:
    portrait:       <image>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>
    message:        <string>
}

添加/修改医嘱
    请在模板文件中标明record_id所在位置
POST /doc/modify_advice
request:
    record_id:      <int>
    advice:         <string>
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>
    message:        <string>
}

修改挂号状态 -- ( 如将‘未就诊’改成‘已就诊’ )
POST /doc/modify_status
request:
    record_id:      <int>
    status:         <int>   // 0 - 未就诊，1 - 已就诊， 2 - 需复诊
response:
{
    error_code:     <int>
    message:        <string>
}